name: Get all Money at the top of THE CRAZY CRYPT
Hit the switch in THE CONSEVATORY from the left side
Kill the Judge with the Sword
Every digit of your score has to be the same except for the last one and score has to be at least 10000
Clear THE MONEY SPIDER by starting from the bottom
Complete THE PIRANHA TANK without taking or dealing damage
Kill the Wacky Scientist with the Golfball
Get all 1UPs in the CRYPTIC CLIMB
Complete the PORTRAIT GALLERY and dont go into THE DARK ROOM
Reach the Boss Door in WORMY WAY by using only ropes
Clear the West and East Chimney normal
Get the Heart at the Bubble Race Part at THE FIRING FISH
